node.text:
With this year being both the 25th anniversary of Pokémon and the fifth anniversary of Pokémon GO, this year’s Pokémon GO Fest is sure to be a special event! #PokemonGOFest2021

Join us as we go behind the scenes with some Niantics who were there when Pokémon GO launched, and learn what it was like when Pokémon GO changed the world in 2016.
Check out this and other #PokemonGOFest2021-themed video and audio content here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/pokemongofest2021-content

Whether you’re a veteran Trainer or just starting your journey with Pokémon GO, everybody has that special Pokémon buddy. 🤩 We’re excited to announce that Trainers and their Buddy Pokémon will soon have more ways to connect, interact, and explore the world.

It’s time for another adventure, Trainers. A #PokemonGOBuddy Adventure. 🤩

Learn more by visiting the link in our bio.
